{"tid":2137794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"跨境貨車周五前須安裝衛星定位　配合內地防控","createTime":"2020-08-03T07:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:07:12.000Z","uid":241764,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"524135e7a4543c995ceedbeea0f5ca88c14500eb","tid":2137794,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"廣東省進一步加強對粵港跨境貨車的管控，要求周五前要安裝衛星定位系統，以配合內地疫情防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n廣東省交通運輸廳發布緊急通知，指為了加強粵港跨境貨車疫情防控工作，要求跨境貨車要在周五前，安裝具有行駛記錄功能的衛星定位裝置。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400325&amp;fbclid=IwAR0qHR5VCRcMVCLKEku13vi2N8McpM5nqJkv1Hnpd7NzZxzQK1xZMJiKv0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400325%26fbclid%3DIwAR0qHR5VCRcMVCLKEku13vi2N8McpM5nqJkv1Hnpd7NzZxzQK1xZMJiKv0k&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=f0adba0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400325%26fbclid%3DIwAR0qHR5VCRcMVCLKEku13vi2N8McpM5nqJkv1Hnpd7NzZxzQK1xZMJiKv0k&h=5eab0568\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400325&amp;fbclid=IwAR0qHR5VCRcMVCLKEku13vi2N8McpM5nqJkv1Hnpd7NzZxzQK1xZMJiKv0k</a><br />\n<br />\n裝係架車到，但個司機會周圍走架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩Catch me if you can ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee9fe20590d84e842945d7bcc671dd20743759e","tid":2137794,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8bbfd7a7432467c5836c471ad09e82d1b040e7","tid":2137794,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"其實依家好多車都有裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{